Brief descriptions of the analysis tools
----------------------------------------

----------
cutden.awk
----------
A script to post-process dat files and discard data with signed densities
less than a minimum or greater than a maximum value.

  user:$ ./cutden.awk min max file.dat > new_file.dat

-----------
cutgrad.awk
-----------
A script to post-process dat files and discard data with reduced density
gradients less than a minimum or greater than a maximum value.

  user:$ ./cutgrad.awk min max file.dat > new_file.dat

--------------
SplitAttRep.py
--------------
A script to separate the attractive an repulsive parts of the 3D NCI surface
stored in the filename-dens.cube and filename-grad.cube files.

  user:$ python SplitAttRep.py filename

